{
  "script_id": "barnsley-fern",
  "voice": "zh-CN-YunxiNeural",
  "voice_key": "yunxi",
  "files": [
    {
      "script_id": "barnsley-fern",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-1",
      "filename": "intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/barnsley-fern/yunxi/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.8,
      "size": 28800,
      "text": "眼前这片翠绿的蕨叶，不是画笔画的，也不是照片。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "barnsley-fern",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/barnsley-fern/yunxi/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.77,
      "size": 28368,
      "text": "它完全由数学生成，只用了四条简单的规则。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "barnsley-fern",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/barnsley-fern/yunxi/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.96,
      "size": 31392,
      "text": "这就是著名的巴恩斯利蕨，分形几何最优雅的例子之一。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "barnsley-fern",
      "section_id": "affine",
      "line_id": "aff-1",
      "filename": "affine-aff-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/barnsley-fern/yunxi/affine-aff-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.12,
      "size": 33984,
      "text": "一切从仿射变换说起，它对一个点做缩放、旋转再平移。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "barnsley-fern",
      "section_id": "affine",
      "line_id": "aff-2",
      "filename": "affine-aff-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/barnsley-fern/yunxi/affine-aff-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.9,
      "size": 30384,
      "text": "每个变换都是六个系数，把当前点搬到一个新位置。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "barnsley-fern",
      "section_id": "affine",
      "line_id": "aff-3",
      "filename": "affine-aff-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/barnsley-fern/yunxi/affine-aff-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.92,
      "size": 30672,
      "text": "巴恩斯利精心挑选了四组系数，各自负责蕨的一个部分。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "barnsley-fern",
      "section_id": "ifs",
      "line_id": "ifs-1",
      "filename": "ifs-ifs-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/barnsley-fern/yunxi/ifs-ifs-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.76,
      "size": 28224,
      "text": "我们从原点出发，反复把变换作用在最新的点上。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "barnsley-fern",
      "section_id": "ifs",
      "line_id": "ifs-2",
      "filename": "ifs-ifs-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/barnsley-fern/yunxi/ifs-ifs-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.02,
      "size": 32256,
      "text": "每一步都产生一个新点，几万步后点云勾勒出整片蕨叶。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "barnsley-fern",
      "section_id": "ifs",
      "line_id": "ifs-3",
      "filename": "ifs-ifs-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/barnsley-fern/yunxi/ifs-ifs-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.0,
      "size": 31968,
      "text": "这种反复自我作用的规则集合，叫做迭代函数系统。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "barnsley-fern",
      "section_id": "probability",
      "line_id": "prob-1",
      "filename": "probability-prob-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/barnsley-fern/yunxi/probability-prob-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.02,
      "size": 32400,
      "text": "关键在于:每一步该用哪个变换，由概率随机决定。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "barnsley-fern",
      "section_id": "probability",
      "line_id": "prob-2",
      "filename": "probability-prob-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/barnsley-fern/yunxi/probability-prob-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.92,
      "size": 30672,
      "text": "主叶变换有百分之八十五的概率，撑起了叶片的主体。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "barnsley-fern",
      "section_id": "probability",
      "line_id": "prob-3",
      "filename": "probability-prob-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/barnsley-fern/yunxi/probability-prob-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.92,
      "size": 30672,
      "text": "而茎变换只有百分之一，恰好细细地画出中央的主干。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "barnsley-fern",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
      "filename": "interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/barnsley-fern/yunxi/interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.21,
      "size": 35280,
      "text": "增加迭代点数，看蕨叶从稀疏的散点逐渐变得饱满清晰。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "barnsley-fern",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-2",
      "filename": "summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/barnsley-fern/yunxi/summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.84,
      "size": 29520,
      "text": "简单的规则，竟涌现出栩栩如生的自然形态。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "barnsley-fern",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-3",
      "filename": "summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/barnsley-fern/yunxi/summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.51,
      "size": 24192,
      "text": "这就是迭代函数系统的魔力，我们下次再见!"
    }
  ],
  "total_duration": 28.67,
